snippet.title: RUN - Trailer Alpha1.2
snippet.description:
RUN is a new roguelite plateformer in which you always have to be fast, jump, run to unlock some new content. Inspired by Celeste, SMB, Dead Cells and Barbie Dreamhouse Adventures.
Alpha available on itch.io : https://runthegame.itch.io/build
